George Magrill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Magrill 0 George Magrill (January 5, 1900 – May 31, 1952) was an American film actor. He appeared in 326 films between 1923 and 1952. He was born in Brooklyn, New York, was married to Ramona Oliver, and had a daughter named Marilynn. Magrill died in Los Angeles, California.
